headline: PACCAR Analyst Day: Parts, Finance Fuel “Stronger” Cycle Profits as 2026 Outlook Holds
summary: PACCAR (NASDAQ:PCAR) executives used the company’s 2026 Investor Conference to emphasize what management described as improved “cycle-over-cycle” financial performance, a growing contribution from parts and financial services, and ongoing investments in manufacturing flexibility and technology.
